t - I know she used to have a coarse apron on over her nice other apron and I can see myself now pulling at this apron. Couldn't bear to have that apron. Oh no, I didn't like - do you know Mrs Hoskinson, many a time if we were poorly she'd light the boile
r night time when she got us to bed and started her washing then. Ye}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15475069\charrsid804585 s. 'Cos that was her awful dread}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 
