No. No never - well my mother had some relation and used to send her this - fruit. Not me mother - me father had relation and he used to send this fruit and got lots of eggs sent to us. So we did very well that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Can you remember any tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
