abbage with a good heart in it. And they pushed things in your bag in them days - as it were - she doesn't want these. Oh put them in. Yes. Awfully kind. They didn't watch the scales going down in them days. Bang would go the scales, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Did they keep any chickens or anything?
