\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1982167\charrsid804585 Oh me mother had to look}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 
 after - after everything. Me brother would bring all sort of - she said she was going to write on - this way to Westons menagerie. We had a cat and a dog and a parrot and a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1982167\charrsid804585 tortoise}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585  and - oh it's -
