Yes. Yes. I did. Yes. Many a time one of us have asked for more and it'd been her share, but she said, our little mouths needed it and she'd cut some bread and butter when we'd gon
e to school and that. And she told us, I mean we didn't know of course. No. Yes, that's true Mrs Hoskinson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Did your father have more?
