\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes, these were the grandchildren.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 So she would go out with her daughters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 
That's right, yes. And she loved to be with them. All - they were all together, I think they were all the family went up this year to Scotland. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Did she do any work for charities or sit on committees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes, they were big - to Liverpool, they were wonderful to Liverpool.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Used to do a lot of charitable work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes, a lot. They had - do you remember the children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid263970\charrsid804585 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 s welfare in Copperers Hill - did you ever hear - well they were - some of the people that started that. With Margaret Reavan. Yes, they were great workers in Liverpool. And against drink. Yes, yes.
