\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Was he abroad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes, he used to be away in America. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 What difference did this make to the household - did it run any differently when he wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang1034\langfe1033\langnp1034\insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 No. No. No. No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 
They were all just longing for the day when he would come home again. Yes. Yes. And he used to come into Mossley Hill station and if it was a decent time some of the
 little children would go - my mother would - she's only like the under nurse - she would take them to Mossley Hill station and - yes. They knew the time he would come.
