\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 So this was something unusual - it wasn't usual for her to be away at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 You said they had many friends calling in this holiday place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Oh they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 They would stay in the house?
