\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes, they did. Yes. Yes, had a very big - lovely ballro}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid227685\charrsid804585 om there. And a great; 
