What do you mean? I don't think - no, I think everybody was very happy and contented going to their little jobs. Yes. All the girls I knew, they were quite happy. Yes, very contented.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 
Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and labourers - did you feel that or not in your working life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 I don't know, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
