\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6829769 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 You lived at home of cour}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid227685\charrsid804585 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 e?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes.
