\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3152901 EW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5202159\charrsid804585 Yes. I used to love that. Walk to the Dingle, get a - a tram car to L}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid227685\charrsid804585 e}{
